#. module: point_of_sale
#: model:ir.model.fields,help:point_of_sale.field_pos_config__amount_authorized_diff
#: model:ir.model.fields,help:point_of_sale.field_res_config_settings__pos_amount_authorized_diff
msgid ""
"This field depicts the maximum difference allowed between the ending balance "
"and the theoretical cash when closing a session, for non-POS managers. If "
"this maximum is reached, the user will have an error message at the closing "
"of his session saying that he needs to contact his manager."
msgstr ""
"ຫ້ອງນີ້ກຳນົດສ່ວນຕ່າງສູງສຸດທີ່ອະນຸຍາດລະຫວ່າງຍອດເຫຼືອປິດຮອບ ແລະ ເງິນສົດຕາມທິດສະດີ "
"ສຳລັບຜູ້ທີ່ບໍ່ແມ່ນຜູ້ຈັດການ POS. ຖ້າເກີນຂີດຈຳກັດນີ້, "
"ຜູ້ໃຊ້ຈະເຫັນຂໍ້ຄວາມແຈ້ງເຕືອນຕອນປິດຮອບວ່າຕ້ອງຕິດຕໍ່ຜູ້ຈັດການ."

#. module: point_of_sale
#: model:ir.model.fields,help:point_of_sale.field_pos_config__group_pos_manager_id
